56
00:04:25,752 --> 00:04:27,151
(If you play in the water again,)

57
00:04:27,151 --> 00:04:28,591
(then you'll go to school barefoot.)

58
00:04:57,352 --> 00:05:00,191
Although my mom always scolded me,

59
00:05:00,591 --> 00:05:04,191
