60
00:05:05,231 --> 00:05:07,191
Ms. Lin is sharp-tongued,
but soft-hearted.

61
00:05:07,472 --> 00:05:08,591
Chen Luzhou's mom

62
00:05:08,912 --> 00:05:10,832
