125
00:10:07,872 --> 00:10:08,592
Zhi.

126
00:10:08,912 --> 00:10:10,431
You know what a crush is?

127
00:10:11,111 --> 00:10:12,151
It means

128
00:10:12,471 --> 00:10:14,912
even though it's
a rainy day you dislike,

129
00:10:15,191 --> 00:10:17,071
