to bail on last time's hotpot?)

243
00:16:37,151 --> 00:16:38,111
(The kind Zhu.)

244
00:16:38,111 --> 00:16:39,071
Got the middle tower.

245
00:16:39,752 --> 00:16:41,752
(Who said I bailed?
I'll treat you next time.)

246
00:16:50,231 --> 00:16:51,872
